00:23:09,083 --> 00:23:10,958
- ♪ I DON'T KNOW ♪

383
00:23:13,041 --> 00:23:14,875
♪ JUST A CHILD ♪

384
00:23:38,625 --> 00:23:40,791
♪ WHY SO WHY? ♪

385
00:23:43,458 --> 00:23:45,083
♪ JUST YOU LIKE ♪

386
00:23:55,875 --> 00:23:59,000
♪ TIP TAPS, TIP TAPS ♪

