00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:02,541
♪ TIP TAPS ♪

388
00:24:02,625 --> 00:24:03,916
♪ SO LET'S SING ♪

389
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:07,916
♪ TIPS TAPS, TIP TAPS ♪

390
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:10,125
♪ TIP TAPS ♪

391
00:24:14,416 --> 00:24:17,083
- Ray: A WOMAN ROBBED
OF HER FUTURE,

392
00:24:17,166 --> 00:24:19,083
